# Force LF line endings on text files for cross-OS consistency.
#
# Without this, Windows checkouts show every text file as modified
# (CRLF on disk vs LF in HEAD), which makes `git status` unusable
# and blocks `git merge`. Binary files are auto-detected by the
# `text=auto` heuristic and excluded from line-ending conversion.
* text=auto eol=lf
